{"tid":2174842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共軍南海發射反艦彈道飛彈　美軍RC-135S偵察機行得正企得正公開偵搜","createTime":"2020-08-26T06:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T07:35:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbedd99fdd8d8c3216719b1949f520d1e6e8fd3","tid":2174842,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:50:32.000Z","msg":"中國解放軍今（26日）在南海進行反艦彈道飛彈試射，美軍一架專門用於追蹤導彈和火箭軌跡的RC-135S偵察機今天上午從巴士海峽往南海進行偵搜，並在近中午左右循原航道飛返駐地，據了解，該架RC-135S偵察機是為了偵搜解放軍發射彈道飛彈的電子參數而來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200826/AU2V2SBOXRFB5BYEENXZQJLJZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200826%2FAU2V2SBOXRFB5BYEENXZQJLJZI%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=32a6e316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200826%2FAU2V2SBOXRFB5BYEENXZQJLJZI%2F&h=48bc71f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200826/AU2V2SBOXRFB5BYEENXZQJLJZI/</a>"},{"pid":"5bf94db69957afd92270decab03ae088fd0d59e9","tid":2174842,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"美國recon 好努力做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ecb2653cb3054b7e850db634ade9292f2b0513","tid":2174842,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"Recon 攔截信號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243d8fce6a96022b439d1700204e30a4e3586b33","tid":2174842,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"50ecb2653cb3054b7e850db634ade9292f2b0513","tid":2174842,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"Recon 攔截信號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />